Class RequestBuffer.RequestFuture<T>

  • java.lang.Object

    Enclosing class:
    RequestBuffer

    public static class RequestBuffer.RequestFuture<T>
extends Object
implements Future<T>, Delayed
    This represents a future request which may or may not have been executed at the time of construction.
